        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Both herbs score 13 from 5 tiles (2.6 per tile). THYME uses H+Y+M, while CHIVE uses C+H+V. They target different awkward tiles, so learn both — when one set of tiles appears on your rack, you'll have the answer ready.</p>
